title: [PS3] GameSonic Manager v3.11 + Light Version
description:
GameSonic Manager v3.11 + Light Version {Standard + SingStar Replacement] 
Orion has released GameSonic Manager v3.11 along with the Standard or SingStar Light version of the backup manager. New in version 3.11 of the manager is the added mamba payload support for 4.41 & 4.46 DEX CFW's, thanks to Joonie's efforts. Joonie has warned me that 3.55 DEX payload was included by mistake and has issues and will not work correctly.
